title: Change of Scheduled Start of Commercial Operation at Tokuyama Hydroelectric Power Station Unit 1 (Chubu ...
text: ( Source : Chubu Electric Power Co Inc) Chubu Electric Power would like to announce that Tokuyama Hydroelectric Power Station Unit 1 's start of commercial operation has been changed to March 2016 from the originally planned September 2015 .
